{"tid":1046390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【發大財】韓國瑜：三月下旬出訪港澳深圳廈門","createTime":"2019-03-04T08:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T10:30:14.000Z","uid":39521,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1a90a3b7e0ddca0156999fd9f823814a3f185da0","tid":1046390,"uid":39521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:14:41.000Z","msg":"在台灣，國民黨籍的高雄市長韓國瑜，今日召開兩岸工作小組會議，席間宣布本月22日至本月28日期間，前往香港、澳門、深圳和廈門4座城市交流。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜表示，此行目的是爭取更多「貨出去人進來」的可能商機與合作機會，並保證行程將尊重台灣現行法令規定，陸委會可放心。他又希望中央行政機關可支持鼓勵高雄，「讓高雄邁開大步走出去，迎接更多商貿機會」。<br />\n<br />\n此次是高雄市兩岸工作小組的第一次會議。有關小組是由韓國瑜擔任召集人，成員包括8位市府首長丶前高雄縣長楊秋興和4位大陸台商會長等。<br />\n<br />\n（中時電子報/聯合新聞網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190304/s00004/1551685069013/%e9%9f%93%e5%9c%8b%e7%91%9c-3%e6%9c%88%e4%b8%8b%e6%97%ac%e5%87%ba%e8%a8%aa%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e6%b7%b1%e5%9c%b3%e5%bb%88%e9%96%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190304%2Fs00004%2F1551685069013%2F%25e9%259f%2593%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%2591%259c-3%25e6%259c%2588%25e4%25b8%258b%25e6%2597%25ac%25e5%2587%25ba%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b7%25b1%25e5%259c%25b3%25e5%25bb%2588%25e9%2596%2580&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4PS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=50e39a1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190304%2Fs00004%2F1551685069013%2F%25e9%259f%2593%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%2591%259c-3%25e6%259c%2588%25e4%25b8%258b%25e6%2597%25ac%25e5%2587%25ba%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b7%25b1%25e5%259c%25b3%25e5%25bb%2588%25e9%2596%2580&h=c6b6ea1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190304/s00004/1551685069013/%e9%9f%93%e5%9c%8b%e7%91%9c-3%e6%9c%88%e4%b8%8b%e6%97%ac%e5%87%ba%e8%a8%aa%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e6%b7%b1%e5%9c%b3%e5%bb%88%e9%96%80</a>"},{"pid":"3d886d9854e113e3b